<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <title>{% block title %}Murim Mania{% endblock %}</title>
        <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 128 128%22><text y=%221.2em%22 font-size=%2296%22>⚔️</text></svg>">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
        <style>
            :root {
                --murim-red: #dc2626;
                --murim-gold: #f59e0b;
                --murim-dark: #1f2937;
                --murim-light: #f8fafc;
            }
            
            body {
                font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f2937 0%, #374151 100%);
                min-height: 100vh;
                color: #333;
            }
            
            .navbar {
                background: rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.95) !important;
                backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
                border-bottom: 2px solid var(--murim-gold);
            }
            
            .navbar-brand {
                color: var(--murim-gold) !important;
                font-weight: bold;
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .navbar-nav .nav-link {
                color: #e5e7eb !important;
                transition: color 0.3s ease;
            }
            
            .navbar-nav .nav-link:hover {
                color: var(--murim-gold) !important;
            }
            
            .main-content {
                background: white;
                border-radius: 15px;
                box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
                margin: 2rem 0;
                overflow: hidden;
            }
            
            .hero-section {
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--murim-red) 0%, #b91c1c 100%);
                color: white;
                padding: 4rem 0;
                text-align: center;
            }
            
            .hero-section h1 {
                font-size: 3rem;
                font-weight: bold;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
                text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            }
            
            .hero-section p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                opacity: 0.9;
            }
            
            .card {
                border: none;
                border-radius: 15px;
                box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
                transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
                overflow: hidden;
            }
            
            .card:hover {
                transform: translateY(-5px);
                box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            }
            
            .card-header {
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--murim-gold) 0%, #d97706 100%);
                color: white;
                border: none;
                font-weight: bold;
            }
            
            .btn-primary {
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--murim-red) 0%, #b91c1c 100%);
                border: none;
                border-radius: 25px;
                padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                transition: all 0.3s ease;
            }
            
            .btn-primary:hover {
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b91c1c 0%, #991b1b 100%);
                transform: translateY(-2px);
                box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.3);
            }
            
            .btn-outline-primary {
                color: var(--murim-red);
                border-color: var(--murim-red);
                border-radius: 25px;
                padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                transition: all 0.3s ease;
            }
            
            .btn-outline-primary:hover {
                background: var(--murim-red);
                border-color: var(--murim-red);
                transform: translateY(-2px);
            }
            
            .category-badge {
                border-radius: 20px;
                padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
                font-size: 0.875rem;
                font-weight: 500;
                color: white;
                text-decoration: none;
                display: inline-block;
                transition: all 0.3s ease;
            }
            
            .category-badge:hover {
                transform: scale(1.05);
                color: white;
                text-decoration: none;
            }
            
            .alert {
                border: none;
                border-radius: 10px;
                padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .alert-success {
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
                color: white;
            }
            
            .alert-danger {
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%);
                color: white;
            }
            
            .form-control {
                border-radius: 10px;
                border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
                padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
                transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
            }
            
            .form-control:focus {
                border-color: var(--murim-gold);
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.2rem rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.25);
            }
            
            .sidebar {
                background: #f8fafc;
                border-radius: 15px;
                padding: 2rem;
                height: fit-content;
            }
            
            .sidebar h5 {
                color: var(--murim-dark);
                font-weight: bold;
                margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            }
            
            .list-group-item {
                border: none;
                background: transparent;
                padding: 0.75rem 0;
                border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            }
            
            .list-group-item:last-child {
                border-bottom: none;
            }
            
            .footer {
                background: var(--murim-dark);
                color: #e5e7eb;
                padding: 3rem 0;
                margin-top: 4rem;
            }
            
            .article-meta {
                color: #6b7280;
                font-size: 0.875rem;
            }
            
            .comment-section {
                background: #f8fafc;
                border-radius: 15px;
                padding: 2rem;
                margin-top: 2rem;
            }
            
            .comment {
                background: white;
                border-radius: 10px;
                padding: 1.5rem;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
                border-left: 4px solid var(--murim-gold);
            }
            
            .comment-author {
                font-weight: bold;
                color: var(--murim-red);
            }
            
            .comment-date {
                color: #6b7280;
                font-size: 0.875rem;
            }
        </style>
        {% block stylesheets %}{% endblock %}
    </head>
    <body>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark fixed-top">
            <div class="container">
                <a class="navbar-brand" href="{{ path('app_home') }}">
                    <i class="fas fa-dragon me-2"></i>Murim Mania
                </a>
                <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
                </button>
                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto">
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_home') }}">
                                <i class="fas fa-home me-1"></i>Accueil
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item">
                            <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_article_index') }}">
                                <i class="fas fa-scroll me-1"></i>Articles
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        {% if app.user %}
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_article_new') }}">
                                    <i class="fas fa-plus me-1"></i>Nouvel Article
                                </a>
                            </li>
                        {% endif %}
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="navbar-nav">
                        {% if app.user %}
                            <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                                <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown">
                                    <i class="fas fa-user me-1"></i>{{ app.user.username }}
                                </a>
                                <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                                    <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="{{ path('app_logout') }}">
                                        <i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt me-1"></i>Déconnexion
                                    </a></li>
                                </ul>
                            </li>
                        {% else %}
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_login') }}">
                                    <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt me-1"></i>Connexion
                                </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="nav-item">
                                <a class="nav-link" href="{{ path('app_register') }}">
                                    <i class="fas fa-user-plus me-1"></i>Inscription
                                </a>
                            </li>
                        {% endif %}
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <div style="padding-top: 80px;">
            <div class="container">
                {% for message in app.flashes('success') %}
                    <div class="alert alert-success alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle me-2"></i>{{ message }}
                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}

                {% for message in app.flashes('error') %}
                    <div class="alert alert-danger alert-dismissible fade show" role="alert">
                        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle me-2"></i>{{ message }}
                        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="alert"></button>
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}

                {% block body %}{% endblock %}
            </div>
        </div>

        <footer class="footer">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <h5><i class="fas fa-dragon me-2"></i>Murim Mania</h5>
                        <p>Explorez les mystères du monde martial et découvrez les secrets de la cultivation.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6 text-md-end">
                        <p>&copy; 2025 Murim Mania - Blog Murim</p>
                        <p><small>Créé avec passion pour le Murim</small></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </footer>

        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
        {% block javascripts %}{% endblock %}
    </body>
</html>